13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Homiladorlik kalkulyatori taxminiy tug'ilish sanasini (TTS), haftalardagi joriy muddatni va trimestrni aniqlaydi. TTS Negele formulasi bo'yicha hisoblanadi: oxirgi hayzning birinchi kuni + 280 kun (40 hafta). O'zbekistonda har yili taxminan 800 000 bola tug'iladi, birinchi marta tug'ayotgan ayollarning o'rtacha yoshi 22-24. Tug'ruqqa yordam ko'rsatish tizimi ayollar maslahatxonalari, tug'ruqxonalar va perinatal markazlarni o'z ichiga oladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Homiladorlik trimestrlari: 1-chi (1-12 hafta) — homila organlarining shakllanishi, birinchi UZI 11-14 haftada; 2-chi (13-27 hafta) — faol o'sish, ikkinchi UZI 18-22 haftada; 3-chi (28-40 hafta) — tug'ruqqa tayyorgarlik, uchinchi UZI 30-34 haftada. Kalkulyator joriy haftani, TTSgacha qolgan kunlarni va tekshiruvlarning asosiy sanalarini ko'rsatadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda homiladorlikni kuzatish poliklinikalardagi ayollar maslahatxonalarida amalga oshiriladi (MTS bo'yicha bepul). Tavsiya etilgan tashrif jadvali: 28 haftagacha — oyda 1 marta, 28-36 hafta — oyda 2 marta, 36 haftadan keyin — har hafta. Majburiy tahlillar: umumiy va biokimyoviy qon tahlili, qon guruhi, rezus-omil, OIV, gepatit, 1 va 2-trimestr skrininglari."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Faqat 5% tug'ilishlar aniq TTSda sodir bo'ladi. Normal tug'ilish — 37-42 hafta. 37 haftagacha tug'ilish muddatidan oldingi, 42 haftadan keyin esa ortiqcha ko'tarilgan hisoblanadi. O'zbekistonda barcha tug'ruqxonalar (tug'ruq majmualari) fuqarolarga bepul yordam ko'rsatadi. Xususiy klinikalar pullik tug'ruq xizmatini taklif etadi: xizmat darajasiga qarab 5 000 000 dan 25 000 000 so'mgacha."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Homiladorlik kalkulyatori barcha bosqichlarni rejalashtirishga yordam beradi: oxirgi hayz birinchi kuni yoki homiladorlik sanasini kiriting. Kalkulyator joriy muddatni, TTSni, UZI va tahlillar sanalarini, shuningdek har haftada bolaning rivojlanishi haqida foydali ma'lumotlarni ko'rsatadi."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],["$","$L18",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4","children":[["$","$L19","0",{"value":"faq-0","children":[["$","$L1a",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Tug'ilish sanasini qanday hisoblash mumkin?"}],["$","$L1b",null,{"children":"$L1c"}]]}],"$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20"]}]]}],"$L21"]}]
